    "body": "## Purpose\n\nSUMMARY:\n* make `prepare_moe_fp8_layer_for_marlin` into a pure function for consistency with other methods and compatibility with the `replace_parameter` semantics that are needed for quantized weight reloading\n* remove size_k_first option (there are no quant methods which use `size_k_first=True`)\n* remove w13_bias permute (there are no quant methods which exploit this functionality (we can add it back if needed)\n\n## Test Plan\n\n```bash\nMODEL_BLOCK := \"Qwen/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B-Instruct-FP8\"\nMODEL_TENSOR := \"amd/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1-FP8-KV\"\nGPUS := \"2\"\nPORT := \"8001\"\n\nlaunch_marlin_block:\n\tVLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 VLLM_TEST_FORCE_FP8_MARLIN=1 chg run --gpus {{GPUS}} -- vllm serve {{MODEL_BLOCK}} -tp {{GPUS}} --port {{PORT}}\n\nlaunch_marlin_tensor:\n\tVLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=0 VLLM_TEST_FORCE_FP8_MARLIN=1 chg run --gpus {{GPUS}} -- vllm serve {{MODEL_TENSOR}} -tp {{GPUS}} --port {{PORT}}\n\neval_block:\n\tlm_eval \\\n\t\t--model local-completions \\\n\t\t--tasks gsm8k \\\n\t\t--model_args \"model={{MODEL_BLOCK}},base_url=http://localhost:{{PORT}}/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False\"\n\neval_tensor:\n\tlm_eval \\\n\t\t--model local-completions \\\n\t\t--tasks gsm8k \\\n\t\t--model_args \"model={{MODEL_TENSOR}},base_url=http://localhost:{{PORT}}/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False\"\n```\n\n## Test Results\n- `fp8.py`\n```bash\nMODEL_BLOCK := \"Qwen/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B-Instruct-FP8\"\nMODEL_TENSOR := \"amd/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1-FP8-KV\"\n```\n\n```bash\nlocal-completions (model=Qwen/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B-Instruct-FP8,base_url=http://localhost:8001/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False), gen_kwargs: (None), limit: None, num_fewshot: None, batch_size: 1\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8681|±  |0.0093|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8878|±  |0.0087|\n```\n\n```bash\nlocal-completions (model=amd/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1-FP8-KV,base_url=http://localhost:8001/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False), gen_kwargs: (None), limit: None, num_fewshot: None, batch_size: 1\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.6558|±  |0.0131|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.6528|±  |0.0131|\n```\n\n- `compressed-tensors`\n```\nMODEL_BLOCK := \"RedHatAI/Qwen3-30B-A3B-FP8-block\"\nMODEL_TENSOR := \"RedHatAI/Llama-4-Scout-17B-16E-Instruct-FP8-dynamic\"\n```\n\n```bash\nlocal-completions (model=RedHatAI/Qwen3-30B-A3B-FP8-block,base_url=http://localhost:8001/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False), gen_kwargs: (None), limit: None, num_fewshot: None, batch_size: 1\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8302|±  |0.0103|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8870|±  |0.0087|\n```\n\n```bash\nlocal-completions (model=RedHatAI/Llama-4-Scout-17B-16E-Instruct-FP8-dynamic,base_url=http://localhost:8001/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False), gen_kwargs: (None), limit: None, num_fewshot: None, batch_size: 1\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.9151|±  |0.0077|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8992|±  |0.0083|\n```\n\n- `quark`\n```\nMODEL_TENSOR := \"amd/Qwen3-30B-A3B-Thinking-2507-ptpc\"\n```\n\n```bash\nlocal-completions (model=amd/Qwen3-30B-A3B-Thinking-2507-ptpc,base_url=http://localhost:8001/v1/completions,num_concurrent=1000,tokenized_requests=False), gen_kwargs: (None), limit: None, num_fewshot: None, batch_size: 1\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.6839|±  |0.0128|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.7915|±  |0.0112|\n```\n\n---\n<details>\n<summary> Essential Elements of an Effective PR Description Checklist </summary>\n\n- [ ] The purpose of the PR, such as \"Fix some issue (link existing issues this PR will resolve)\".\n- [ ] The test plan, such as providing test command.\n- [ ] The test results, such as pasting the results comparison before and after, or e2e results\n- [ ] (Optional) The necessary documentation update, such as updating `supported_models.md` and `examples` for a new model.\n- [ ] (Optional) Release notes update. If your change is user facing, please update the release notes draft in the [Google Doc](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YyVqrgX4gHTtrstbq8oWUImOyPCKSGnJ7xtTpmXzlRs/edit?tab=t.0).\n</details>\n\n",
